      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIRE AND GRAVY (8) boasts a strong record this course with six wins and three minors from 14 tries. Was out of placings last time (22.13) at Q Lakeside in a Free For All, finishing fifth and beaten 6 lengths. Rates on top and should go close. MAJESTIC EMMY (5) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her slick win the start prior, getting around Taree Super Track over 300m in 17.42. Has the ability and looks a key chance. OTHELLO (7) recorded his best time this course and distance latest, finishing a one length second behind Striped Mac in 25.48. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. MISTY BONUS (4) jumped best and was never headed last time. Sure to figure prominently.",
